nfrequency are observed. As a consequence, the electron heating is strongly\nenhanced by the presence of PSR oscillations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Feb 2016 19:41:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-12"}
