as yet no general agreement with simulation results based on the latter\nmethodology. We also propose a new method to directly calculate the electrolyte\nstandard chemical potential in the Henry-Law ideality model. We conclude by\nmaking recommendations for calculating solubility, chemical potentials and\nactivity coefficients, and outline a potential path for future progress.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Feb 2016 14:26:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Mar 2016 15:15:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-29"}
